00:25:41.908 --> 00:25:44.230 align:middle line:90%


00:25:44.230 --> 00:25:47.200 align:middle line:84%
I try to say the
same thing wherever

00:25:47.200 --> 00:25:51.070 align:middle line:84%
I go, which is that it is a
basic human question-- maybe,

00:25:51.070 --> 00:25:53.920 align:middle line:84%
the basic human question--
to ask, what is it

00:25:53.920 --> 00:25:55.030 align:middle line:90%
around the next corner?

00:25:55.030 --> 00:25:56.650 align:middle line:90%
What is it just over that hill?

00:25:56.650 --> 00:25:58.360 align:middle line:90%
What's going on over there?

00:25:58.360 --> 00:26:00.250 align:middle line:84%
I want to understand
how things work

00:26:00.250 --> 00:26:01.390 align:middle line:90%
and where things come from.

00:26:01.390 --> 00:26:05.230 align:middle line:10%
And I'm attracted to esoteric
and alternative spirituality

00:26:05.230 --> 00:26:07.480 align:middle line:10%
because those spiritual
movements more

00:26:07.480 --> 00:26:12.280 align:middle line:10%
than any other in modern life
have presented practical ideas

00:26:12.280 --> 00:26:14.300 align:middle line:10%
and methods to the individual.

00:26:14.300 --> 00:26:17.050 align:middle line:84%
And if my work
can help people, I

00:26:17.050 --> 00:26:20.500 align:middle line:84%
hope it will give them
a sense of options.

00:26:20.500 --> 00:26:22.660 align:middle line:84%
I hope it will give
them a sense of freedom

00:26:22.660 --> 00:26:24.520 align:middle line:90%
to experiment with these things.

00:26:24.520 --> 00:26:27.250 align:middle line:84%
I hope that if they've
had a disappointment

00:26:27.250 --> 00:26:29.980 align:middle line:84%
in their experiments,
they can realize

00:26:29.980 --> 00:26:33.070 align:middle line:84%
that that disappointment
is not something that they

00:26:33.070 --> 00:26:34.720 align:middle line:90%
should blame themselves for.

00:26:34.720 --> 00:26:36.940 align:middle line:84%
Or is not reason to
pack up their bags

00:26:36.940 --> 00:26:38.170 align:middle line:90%
and go somewhere else.

00:26:38.170 --> 00:26:39.460 align:middle line:90%
But stick around.

00:26:39.460 --> 00:26:40.270 align:middle line:90%
Stay with us.

00:26:40.270 --> 00:26:43.120 align:middle line:84%
That disappointment is part
of a lifelong experiment.

00:26:43.120 --> 00:26:46.660 align:middle line:84%
That's the beauty
of your existence.

00:26:46.660 --> 00:26:49.750 align:middle line:84%
We are here-- if we're
here for anything--

00:26:49.750 --> 00:26:53.020 align:middle line:84%
to be generative, to
experiment, to probe.

00:26:53.020 --> 00:26:56.260 align:middle line:84%
So how can you have
experimentation

00:26:56.260 --> 00:26:59.140 align:middle line:84%
without a null
experiment at some point?

00:26:59.140 --> 00:27:01.360 align:middle line:84%
Without what looks like
a failure at some point?

00:27:01.360 --> 00:27:03.640 align:middle line:84%
That may be the stepping
stone to some extraordinary

00:27:03.640 --> 00:27:06.249 align:middle line:84%
discovery, including
a discovery that

00:27:06.249 --> 00:27:07.790 align:middle line:84%
could help the search
of other people

00:27:07.790 --> 00:27:11.800 align:middle line:84%
because we need to find out
under what conditions do

00:27:11.800 --> 00:27:13.900 align:middle line:90%
certain spiritual ideas work?

00:27:13.900 --> 00:27:16.570 align:middle line:84%
Under what conditions do
they not seem to work?

00:27:16.570 --> 00:27:18.100 align:middle line:90%
I want people to be practical.

00:27:18.100 --> 00:27:19.600 align:middle line:90%
I want people to be probing.

00:27:19.600 --> 00:27:21.700 align:middle line:84%
I want people to
be experimental.

00:27:21.700 --> 00:27:26.770 align:middle line:84%
And above all, I want people
to be civil, and meticulous,

00:27:26.770 --> 00:27:29.140 align:middle line:84%
and decorous in how
they think and how

00:27:29.140 --> 00:27:31.000 align:middle line:84%
they talk to one
another because that

00:27:31.000 --> 00:27:36.060 align:middle line:84%
has enormous impact
on your experience.

00:27:36.060 --> 00:27:46.539 align:middle line:90%